# ============================================================
# STM32CubeIDE .gitignore
# Intentionally keeps CMSIS, HAL driver source, startup files,
# and .ioc config — these are committed on purpose to document
# what CubeMX/CubeIDE auto-generates (see project 01 vs 03).
# Only build output and local IDE/workspace noise is excluded.
# ============================================================

# --- Build output ---
Debug/
Release/
build/
*.o
*.obj
*.elf
*.bin
*.hex
*.map
*.list
*.su
*.d
*.i
*.lst

# --- STM32CubeIDE workspace / project-local metadata ---
# .cproject and .project are usually fine to keep (they define
# the CDT project itself), but .settings can contain local
# machine-specific paths — safe to ignore.
.settings/
*.launch
.metadata/
.cproject
.project

# --- STM32CubeMX backup/log noise ---
*.ioc.bak
*_HAL_settings.txt
*.mxproject

# --- OS / editor junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
